original_title: WWE: The Rock: The Most Electrifying Man in Sports Entertainment - Vol. 3
overview: THE ROCK: THE MOST ELECTRIFYING MAN IN SPORTS ENTERTAINMENT - VOL. 3 chronicles the greatest matches in Rock's historic WWE career. Relive some of the most significant bouts in the Great One's career. Volume 3 highlights include Rock's legendary WrestleMania X8 match with Hulk Hogan, his final WrestleMania battle with Stone Cold Steve Austin, as well as a collection of 16 of his most memorable interviews and promos.
title: WWE: The Rock: The Most Electrifying Man in Sports Entertainment - Vol. 3
